I'M JUST chased five then four wide under coaxing from the five-sixteenths, angled six wide into upper stretch, improved position for the last major share. OCTOBER BLISS five paths off the inside down the backstretch, tucked three wide into the turn, came under coaxing near the three-eighths and got directed inwards by the rider forcing MUDVILLE NINE to check sharply off his heels in the two path at that station, spun two to three wide for home and weakened in the stretch. TUNNEL VISION four then three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing at the seven-sixteenths, swung four wide for home and weakened. ART OF COURAGE got bumped at the start by RUNANDSCORE and in turn bumped WHO ME, dueled inside of LIFTIME OF CHANCE, came under coaxing at the three-eighths and yielded the front with five-sixteenths to go, took the inside route into upper stretch and faltered. MUDVILLE NINE chased three then two wide from mid pack, came under coaxing near the three-eighths and was forced to check sharply off the heels of OCTOBER BLISS when that foe came in and impeded him at the three-eighths, lost all momentum as a result and was guided quietly along while tiring to the end. ZEALOUS LEGACY chased three to four wide under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, swung four wide into upper stretch, and gave way. WHO ME got bumped at the start by ART OF COURAGE due to pressure from RUNANDSCORE breaking inwards, chased along the inside down the backstretch, tipped out two then three wide briefly under coaxing at the seven-sixteenths before being placed to a protective hold, got guided further outside cantering eight wide into upper stretch eased up, then got pulled up in the vicinity of the three-sixteenths marker and was subsequently vanned off.
